text: Takht-e-Nasarati is an administrative subdivision (tehsil) of Karak District in Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan. The town of Takht-e-Nasrati is the headquarters of the tehsil. ==Administration== The tehsil is administratively divided into 7 Union Councils - one of which makes up the tehsil capital. These are: * Ahmad Abad * Chowkara * Jehangiri * Mianki Banda * Shanawa Godi Khel * Siraj Khel * Takht-E-Nasrati * Shaheedan Banda Category:Tehsils of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Category:Karak District
title: Takht-e-Nasrati Tehsil
